title: Bug: Display property not taking effect in new PDF emitter
description: The display property of an item is not taking effect in the new PDF emitter.
OB: When the display property of an item is set to 'none', it is not being hidden in the new PDF emitter.
EB: When the display property of an item is set to 'none', it should be hidden in the new PDF emitter.
SR:
Steps to Reproduce: 
1. Add a label to the PDF emitter.
2. Open the 'properties' view of the label.
3. Set the sectionDisplay property to 'none'.
4. Generate a new PDF using the emitter and verify that the label is hidden.
